701
00:38:39,659 --> 00:38:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] On je svet.

702
00:38:42,579 --> 00:38:45,420
[SPEAKER_00] I Pavao daje jedan okvir.

703
00:38:45,420 --> 00:38:46,300
[SPEAKER_00] To je najvažnija stvar

704
00:38:46,300 --> 00:38:47,659
[SPEAKER_00] koju morate znati u proroštvu.

705
00:38:47,659 --> 00:38:48,260
[SPEAKER_00] Najvažnija.

706
00:38:48,260 --> 00:38:50,300
[SPEAKER_00] Proročka riječ

707
00:38:50,300 --> 00:38:51,639
[SPEAKER_00] te izgrađuje,

708
00:38:51,639 --> 00:38:53,579
[SPEAKER_00] te tješi

709
00:38:53,579 --> 00:38:54,900
[SPEAKER_00] i ohrabruje.

710
00:38:54,900 --> 00:38:56,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ok?

711
00:38:56,559 --> 00:38:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] I sve što Božja riječ radi

712
00:38:58,539 --> 00:38:59,340
[SPEAKER_00] u našem životu

713
00:38:59,340 --> 00:39:00,599
[SPEAKER_00] ide kroz ove tri stvari.

714
00:39:00,599 --> 00:39:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] Izgrađuje te,

715
00:39:03,199 --> 00:39:04,300
[SPEAKER_00] tješi i ohrabruje.

716
00:39:04,300 --> 00:39:05,639
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je to lijepo.

717
00:39:05,639 --> 00:39:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] Čak i da si umisliš nešto

718
00:39:07,519 --> 00:39:08,679
[SPEAKER_00] što ćete izgraditi,

719
00:39:08,679 --> 00:39:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] ne možeš to bez Božjeg duha.

720
00:39:10,079 --> 00:39:11,780
[SPEAKER_00] Jer jedino Božji duh

721
00:39:11,780 --> 00:39:12,480
[SPEAKER_00] u ovom svijetu

722
00:39:12,480 --> 00:39:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] može nekog izgraditi.

723
00:39:13,539 --> 00:39:15,719
[SPEAKER_00] Šta imaš da se primio?

724
00:39:15,719 --> 00:39:17,639
[SPEAKER_00] Čak i oni koji ne vjeruju

725
00:39:17,639 --> 00:39:18,460
[SPEAKER_00] Boga se izgrađuju

726
00:39:18,460 --> 00:39:19,280
[SPEAKER_00] zato ovim Bog daje.

727
00:39:19,280 --> 00:39:22,900
[SPEAKER_00] Čak i ako pogriješiš

728
00:39:22,900 --> 00:39:24,820
[SPEAKER_00] u raspoznanju riječi

729
00:39:24,820 --> 00:39:25,599
[SPEAKER_00] Božji nije problem.

730
00:39:25,599 --> 00:39:27,699
[SPEAKER_00] A Bog ti želi,

731
00:39:27,699 --> 00:39:28,760
[SPEAKER_00] On te želi izgraditi,

732
00:39:28,760 --> 00:39:29,619
[SPEAKER_00] želi te tješiti

733
00:39:29,619 --> 00:39:31,219
[SPEAKER_00] i želi to ohrabret.

734
00:39:31,219 --> 00:39:32,500
[SPEAKER_00] I sad zamislite

735
00:39:32,500 --> 00:39:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] koliko imamo lažnih proroka

736
00:39:34,599 --> 00:39:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] u svijetu

737
00:39:35,079 --> 00:39:37,320
[SPEAKER_00] koji siju strah i osudu.

738
00:39:37,320 --> 00:39:38,800
[SPEAKER_00] To nije siguro

739
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] duha Božjeg.

740
00:39:39,559 --> 00:39:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] Duh Božji uvijek

741
00:39:41,980 --> 00:39:43,119
[SPEAKER_00] podiže,

742
00:39:43,119 --> 00:39:44,179
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek ohrabruje,

743
00:39:44,179 --> 00:39:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek izgrađuje.

744
00:39:45,380 --> 00:39:47,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ste i kad ušli u molitvu

745
00:39:47,619 --> 00:39:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] i kad je bilo ono

746
00:39:48,480 --> 00:39:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] pomazanje,

747
00:39:49,039 --> 00:39:50,280
[SPEAKER_00] pa odlaze ti sve one

748
00:39:50,280 --> 00:39:51,519
[SPEAKER_00] tvoje ljudske logike.

749
00:39:51,519 --> 00:39:53,360
[SPEAKER_00] Sve to odlazi,

750
00:39:53,360 --> 00:39:54,940
[SPEAKER_00] sva naše osude,

751
00:39:54,940 --> 00:39:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] strahovi,

752
00:39:55,599 --> 00:39:56,099
[SPEAKER_00] sram,

753
00:39:56,099 --> 00:39:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] naše gluposti,

754
00:39:57,519 --> 00:39:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] naša ljudsko sargstvo,

755
00:39:59,099 --> 00:39:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] naša logika,

756
00:39:59,900 --> 00:40:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] naš razum

757
00:40:00,519 --> 00:40:02,719
[SPEAKER_00] odlazi i uvijek je Bog

758
00:40:02,719 --> 00:40:04,239
[SPEAKER_00] onaj koji podiže,

759
00:40:04,239 --> 00:40:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] koji te hrabri,

760
00:40:06,079 --> 00:40:07,440
[SPEAKER_00] koji vjeruje u tebe,

761
00:40:07,440 --> 00:40:08,719
[SPEAKER_00] koji ti otkriva

762
00:40:08,719 --> 00:40:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] tvoje sinost,

763
00:40:09,500 --> 00:40:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] tvoje njegovu ljubav za tebe.

764
00:40:12,320 --> 00:40:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] I kad proroci prorokuju,

765
00:40:13,940 --> 00:40:16,280
[SPEAKER_00] a svi ste proroci,

766
00:40:16,280 --> 00:40:17,420
[SPEAKER_00] svi možete prorokovat,

767
00:40:17,420 --> 00:40:18,039
[SPEAKER_00] kaže Pao,

768
00:40:18,039 --> 00:40:19,559
[SPEAKER_00] svi mogu prorokovat.

769
00:40:19,559 --> 00:40:20,840
[SPEAKER_00] To je vrhonska stvar,

770
00:40:20,840 --> 00:40:21,780
[SPEAKER_00] rekao sam to preolako,

771
00:40:21,780 --> 00:40:22,639
[SPEAKER_00] ali jej,

772
00:40:22,639 --> 00:40:24,179
[SPEAKER_00] svi možemo prorokovat.

773
00:40:24,179 --> 00:40:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] Znači svako od vas

774
00:40:25,699 --> 00:40:27,260
[SPEAKER_00] može doći na molitvenom sastanku,

775
00:40:27,260 --> 00:40:27,980
[SPEAKER_00] na ovaj mikrofon

776
00:40:27,980 --> 00:40:28,679
[SPEAKER_00] i prorokovat.

777
00:40:28,679 --> 00:40:31,860
[SPEAKER_00] Kroz ovaj okvir.

778
00:40:31,860 --> 00:40:34,460
[SPEAKER_00] Svi možete čuti Boži glas.

779
00:40:34,460 --> 00:40:37,360
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da smo u početku bebe,

780
00:40:37,360 --> 00:40:39,099
[SPEAKER_00] pa moramo učiti.

781
00:40:39,099 --> 00:40:40,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ali što više učimo,

782
00:40:40,659 --> 00:40:41,860
[SPEAKER_00] to ćemo ga lakše razumjeti.

783
00:40:42,320 --> 00:40:42,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže Isus,

784
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:44,500
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam pastir Dobri,

785
00:40:44,500 --> 00:40:45,699
[SPEAKER_00] vi ste moje ovce

786
00:40:45,699 --> 00:40:46,619
[SPEAKER_00] i ovce moje

787
00:40:46,619 --> 00:40:49,420
[SPEAKER_00] slušaju moj glas.

788
00:40:49,420 --> 00:40:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ti si ovca

789
00:40:51,559 --> 00:40:53,039
[SPEAKER_00] i možeš slušati glas.

790
00:40:53,039 --> 00:40:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] Čestita.

791
00:40:55,460 --> 00:40:57,480
[SPEAKER_00] Mnogi danas to prvi put

792
00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:58,599
[SPEAKER_00] valjda čuju u svom životu.

793
00:40:58,599 --> 00:40:59,760
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ti želi govoriti,

794
00:40:59,760 --> 00:41:01,280
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ti se želi otkriti.

795
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to ne je bilo kakav Bog,

796
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:03,780
[SPEAKER_00] nego Otac.

797
00:41:03,780 --> 00:41:05,900
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ste vi,

798
00:41:05,900 --> 00:41:07,059
[SPEAKER_00] koliko ljudi danas pati

799
00:41:07,059 --> 00:41:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] od bezočinstva.

800
00:41:08,039 --> 00:41:10,219
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko autoriteta je

801
00:41:10,219 --> 00:41:13,239
[SPEAKER_00] totalno loše odradilo

802
00:41:13,239 --> 00:41:13,760
[SPEAKER_00] svoj posao.

803
00:41:13,760 --> 00:41:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko očeva.

804
00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] Živimo u vremenu

805
00:41:15,900 --> 00:41:18,360
[SPEAKER_00] baš napuklih obitelji,

806
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:19,440
[SPEAKER_00] slomljenih.

807
00:41:19,440 --> 00:41:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] Očevi odlaze.

808
00:41:20,619 --> 00:41:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ako su i tu,

809
00:41:22,500 --> 00:41:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] često puta su katastrofa očevi.

810
00:41:24,960 --> 00:41:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] Nepotpuni.

811
00:41:29,039 --> 00:41:30,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ali Bog je naš Otac.

812
00:41:30,239 --> 00:41:32,760
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je čudesan.

813
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:34,659
[SPEAKER_00] I želi ti priča,

814
00:41:34,659 --> 00:41:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] želi ti sve dati.

815
00:41:35,500 --> 00:41:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] I sad,

816
00:41:36,139 --> 00:41:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] jedna od odlika

817
00:41:37,079 --> 00:41:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] duha proroštva je

818
00:41:38,119 --> 00:41:39,840
[SPEAKER_00] jedna kreativnost

819
00:41:39,840 --> 00:41:40,719
[SPEAKER_00] koju duh sveti ima

820
00:41:40,719 --> 00:41:42,099
[SPEAKER_00] da ti daje ono sve

821
00:41:42,099 --> 00:41:42,940
[SPEAKER_00] što ti je potrebno.

822
00:41:42,940 --> 00:41:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] Jer u Kristu imamo

823
00:41:44,119 --> 00:41:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] sve, imamo obilje.

824
00:41:44,920 --> 00:41:46,960
[SPEAKER_00] I znate što će danas

825
00:41:46,960 --> 00:41:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] duh sveti stavljati

826
00:41:47,960 --> 00:41:49,219
[SPEAKER_00] ljudima na srce?

827
00:41:49,219 --> 00:41:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] Točno tamo gdje crkva

828
00:41:50,900 --> 00:41:51,619
[SPEAKER_00] nije izgrađena,

829
00:41:51,619 --> 00:41:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] gdje nije ohrabrena

830
00:41:52,619 --> 00:41:53,219
[SPEAKER_00] i utješena.

831
00:41:53,219 --> 00:41:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] I danas niko ne znaje

832
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] bolje o ovo vrijeme

833
00:41:58,960 --> 00:42:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] i ljude od duha sveti.

834
00:42:00,059 --> 00:42:00,900
[SPEAKER_00] On sve proniče

835
00:42:00,900 --> 00:42:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] i dubina je Božje.

836
00:42:02,019 --> 00:42:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] I on zna što je potrebno.

837
00:42:03,380 --> 00:42:04,219
[SPEAKER_00] I čući,

838
00:42:04,219 --> 00:42:05,679
[SPEAKER_00] znaćete da neki prorok

839
00:42:05,679 --> 00:42:07,219
[SPEAKER_00] kad prepoznaje znako vremena

840
00:42:07,219 --> 00:42:08,440
[SPEAKER_00] i tamo gdje je crkva izgrađena,

841
00:42:08,440 --> 00:42:09,559
[SPEAKER_00] proročki glašće ga

842
00:42:09,559 --> 00:42:10,840
[SPEAKER_00] izgrađivaće crkvu.

843
00:42:10,840 --> 00:42:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] Neće govoriti proti nje.

844
00:42:12,579 --> 00:42:14,739
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ćete čuti

845
00:42:14,739 --> 00:42:15,659
[SPEAKER_00] da vam Bog dolazi

846
00:42:15,659 --> 00:42:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] ako neko muči

847
00:42:16,760 --> 00:42:17,920
[SPEAKER_00] bez očinstvo.

848
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ako neko sluša

849
00:42:19,500 --> 00:42:20,139
[SPEAKER_00] Boži glaz

850
00:42:20,139 --> 00:42:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] za osobu koju muči

851
00:42:22,619 --> 00:42:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] i duški duh će siguro reći

852
00:42:24,059 --> 00:42:26,659
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam tvoj otac.

853
00:42:26,659 --> 00:42:28,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si moje ljubljeno dijete.

854
00:42:28,119 --> 00:42:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] Nisi sam.

855
00:42:29,559 --> 00:42:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nikad te neću ostaviti.

856
00:42:32,000 --> 00:42:34,059
[SPEAKER_00] Vidim što prolaziš.

857
00:42:34,059 --> 00:42:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] Vidim tvoje boli.

858
00:42:35,079 --> 00:42:37,260
[SPEAKER_00] Nijedna nije propala.

859
00:42:37,260 --> 00:42:39,099
[SPEAKER_00] Sve ih skupljam.

860
00:42:39,099 --> 00:42:40,599
[SPEAKER_00] O svima brinem.

861
00:42:40,599 --> 00:42:42,559
[SPEAKER_00] To je proroštvo.

862
00:42:42,559 --> 00:42:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Budućnost je svjetla

863
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] u mojim rukama.

864
00:42:45,960 --> 00:42:47,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam što ću s tobom.

865
00:42:47,320 --> 00:42:49,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ja imam poslanje za tebe.

866
00:42:49,400 --> 00:42:50,800
[SPEAKER_00] Nisi slučaj.

867
00:42:51,260 --> 00:42:52,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam te stvarao

868
00:42:52,739 --> 00:42:53,860
[SPEAKER_00] u majčnoj utrobi.

869
00:42:53,860 --> 00:42:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam ti poznavao dane

870
00:42:55,739 --> 00:42:57,119
[SPEAKER_00] dok još ne bijaše nijednoga.

871
00:42:57,119 --> 00:43:00,840
[SPEAKER_00] Duh sveti koji vidi potrebe

872
00:43:00,840 --> 00:43:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] ovog svijeta.

873
00:43:01,500 --> 00:43:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] Vidi potrebe čovjeka.

874
00:43:02,619 --> 00:43:03,599
[SPEAKER_00] Vidi naše potrebe.

875
00:43:03,599 --> 00:43:04,780
[SPEAKER_00] On to želi.

876
00:43:04,780 --> 00:43:05,699
[SPEAKER_00] On želi doći

877
00:43:05,699 --> 00:43:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] i želi ozdravi.

878
00:43:07,519 --> 00:43:08,159
[SPEAKER_00] Želi izcijeli.

879
00:43:08,159 --> 00:43:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] Želi osloboditi.

880
00:43:09,079 --> 00:43:11,139
[SPEAKER_00] Želi učiniti čudo.

881
00:43:11,139 --> 00:43:12,840
[SPEAKER_00] Želi vam pričati.

882
00:43:12,840 --> 00:43:14,360
[SPEAKER_00] Želi vas uvesti

883
00:43:14,360 --> 00:43:15,800
[SPEAKER_00] u dostojanstvo vaše grštenja.

884
00:43:15,800 --> 00:43:17,400
[SPEAKER_00] Želi vas kao sinove i kćeri.

885
00:43:17,400 --> 00:43:19,820
[SPEAKER_00] Kao kraljave, svećenike i proroke.

886
00:43:19,820 --> 00:43:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] kao ljude punine

887
00:43:21,380 --> 00:43:23,800
[SPEAKER_00] koji idu, osvajaju svijet.

888
00:43:23,800 --> 00:43:25,619
[SPEAKER_00] A kakvi smo mi često?

889
00:43:25,619 --> 00:43:27,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ranjeni.

890
00:43:27,239 --> 00:43:29,360
[SPEAKER_00] Znate što dolazi danas?

891
00:43:29,360 --> 00:43:30,960
[SPEAKER_00] Di su najčešće lažni proroci

892
00:43:30,960 --> 00:43:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] o kojima Pao već mora pisati

893
00:43:32,559 --> 00:43:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] tamo u 1951. godine.

894
00:43:36,500 --> 00:43:37,860
[SPEAKER_00] Jako puno danas.

895
00:43:37,860 --> 00:43:40,800
[SPEAKER_00] Đavao vidi potrebe ljudi.

896
00:43:40,800 --> 00:43:41,940
[SPEAKER_00] Znate što im dolazi?

897
00:43:41,940 --> 00:43:43,099
[SPEAKER_00] Da im lažno evanđelje.

898
00:43:43,099 --> 00:43:45,159
[SPEAKER_00] Malo istine

899
00:43:45,159 --> 00:43:46,039
[SPEAKER_00] i onda ih uništi.

900
00:43:46,039 --> 00:43:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] Počnu se vrti oko svojih rana i potreba.

901
00:43:48,159 --> 00:43:51,699
[SPEAKER_00] On im ponudi neki svoj lijek.

902
00:43:51,699 --> 00:43:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] Odvuče ih od oca,

903
00:43:53,920 --> 00:43:55,280
[SPEAKER_00] od izvora, od žive vode.

904
00:43:55,280 --> 00:43:57,179
[SPEAKER_00] Duh proroštva

905
00:43:57,179 --> 00:43:58,739
[SPEAKER_00] vraća čovjeka Bogu.

906
00:43:59,559 --> 00:44:00,800
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ću vam reći neke odlike

907
00:44:00,800 --> 00:44:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] proroške riječi.

908
00:44:01,880 --> 00:44:06,300
[SPEAKER_00] I sve ove odlike

909
00:44:06,300 --> 00:44:08,500
[SPEAKER_00] prolaze koroz Pavlov trolist.

910
00:44:08,500 --> 00:44:10,099
[SPEAKER_00] Izgrađivanja, ohrabrenja

911
00:44:10,099 --> 00:44:11,360
[SPEAKER_00] i utjehe.

912
00:44:11,360 --> 00:44:14,360
[SPEAKER_00] Proroštvo stavlja u središte

913
00:44:14,360 --> 00:44:16,300
[SPEAKER_00] osobe, u središte života

914
00:44:16,300 --> 00:44:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] i molitve osobu Isusa Hrista,

915
00:44:17,960 --> 00:44:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] ne osobu.

916
00:44:18,579 --> 00:44:21,820
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je u središtu.

917
00:44:21,820 --> 00:44:24,679
[SPEAKER_00] Proroška riječ uzvisuje Hrista.

918
00:44:24,679 --> 00:44:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] Proroška riječ donosi svetost.

919
00:44:29,559 --> 00:44:33,739
[SPEAKER_00] Vraća strah Boži.

920
00:44:33,739 --> 00:44:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ne da se bojimo Boga,

921
00:44:36,460 --> 00:44:37,780
[SPEAKER_00] nego da nam je to,

922
00:44:37,780 --> 00:44:40,440
[SPEAKER_00] počinjemo se brinuti o Bogu,

923
00:44:40,440 --> 00:44:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] o Božim zakonima,

924
00:44:41,480 --> 00:44:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] Božim stvarima.

925
00:44:42,380 --> 00:44:44,519
[SPEAKER_00] Postajemo raspoloživi za Boga.

926
00:44:44,519 --> 00:44:47,320
[SPEAKER_00] Postajemo poučljivi za Božje stvari.

927
00:44:47,320 --> 00:44:48,780
[SPEAKER_00] To je strah Boži.

928
00:44:48,780 --> 00:44:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] To je plemenitost našeg duha

929
00:44:50,440 --> 00:44:51,920
[SPEAKER_00] da želimo Božje

930
00:44:51,920 --> 00:44:53,239
[SPEAKER_00] i da nam je stalo do Božje.

931
00:44:53,239 --> 00:44:57,679
[SPEAKER_00] Proroška riječ širi kraljevstvo Božje.

932
00:44:59,559 --> 00:45:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] Proroška riječ je za crkvu,

933
00:45:01,880 --> 00:45:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] jer izgrađuje crkvu,

934
00:45:03,460 --> 00:45:05,159
[SPEAKER_00] i to Pavao kaže u prvoj korinčanima,

935
00:45:05,159 --> 00:45:08,239
[SPEAKER_00] ona nije za nevjernike.

936
00:45:08,239 --> 00:45:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] Služba jest.

937
00:45:10,119 --> 00:45:11,400
[SPEAKER_00] Vršimo u svijetu,

938
00:45:11,400 --> 00:45:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] za znak svijetu.

939
00:45:13,539 --> 00:45:15,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ali proroška riječ u crkvi

940
00:45:15,219 --> 00:45:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] izgrađuje tještio hrabroje vjernike.

941
00:45:16,920 --> 00:45:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pavao kaže,

942
00:45:17,559 --> 00:45:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] ako i dođe nevjernik

943
00:45:18,619 --> 00:45:20,039
[SPEAKER_00] na ovakav moletveni sastanak,

944
00:45:20,039 --> 00:45:22,219
[SPEAKER_00] tajne se njegovog srca očituju

945
00:45:22,219 --> 00:45:23,940
[SPEAKER_00] i njegovoga srca obtužuje.

946
00:45:23,940 --> 00:45:26,139
[SPEAKER_00] I on će klekniti i reći,

947
00:45:26,139 --> 00:45:26,900
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje ima Bog.

948
00:45:26,900 --> 00:45:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nije proroška riječ

949
00:45:29,500 --> 00:45:30,579
[SPEAKER_00] nam je na nevjernicima,

950
00:45:30,579 --> 00:45:31,639
[SPEAKER_00] jer njega neće to izgraditi,

951
00:45:31,639 --> 00:45:32,400
[SPEAKER_00] tještio hrabrit,

952
00:45:32,400 --> 00:45:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] nego će ga obratiti,

953
00:45:34,000 --> 00:45:35,239
[SPEAKER_00] ali nas,

954
00:45:35,239 --> 00:45:36,579
[SPEAKER_00] nas treba izgraditi,

955
00:45:36,579 --> 00:45:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] tještio hrabrit.

956
00:45:37,820 --> 00:45:39,400
[SPEAKER_00] Proroška riječ je za crkvu

957
00:45:39,400 --> 00:45:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] i mora izgrađivati crkvu.

958
00:45:40,960 --> 00:45:42,340
[SPEAKER_00] Kad vidite nekoga

959
00:45:42,340 --> 00:45:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] ko za sebe tvrdi da je prorok,

960
00:45:44,000 --> 00:45:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] da ima velika otkrivenja

961
00:45:45,099 --> 00:45:46,219
[SPEAKER_00] za posljednje vremena,

962
00:45:46,219 --> 00:45:47,360
[SPEAKER_00] ovako, onako,

963
00:45:47,360 --> 00:45:48,639
[SPEAKER_00] i sije strah

964
00:45:48,639 --> 00:45:51,019
[SPEAKER_00] i obtužuje crku,

965
00:45:51,019 --> 00:45:54,019
[SPEAKER_00] ne dijelio na nju tako da izgrađuje,

966
00:45:54,019 --> 00:45:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] hrabruje i tješi,

967
00:45:55,000 --> 00:45:55,579
[SPEAKER_00] vjerujte mi,

968
00:45:55,579 --> 00:45:56,599
[SPEAKER_00] to nije proroški duh.

969
00:45:56,599 --> 00:45:58,280
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek ima problema.

970
00:45:58,280 --> 00:46:01,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ima gadnih problema.

971
00:46:01,099 --> 00:46:03,780
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Kristov duh ljubi crkvu.

972
00:46:03,780 --> 00:46:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kristov duh je odveo njega na križ.

973
00:46:07,820 --> 00:46:10,059
[SPEAKER_00] Razapio se za svoju zaručnicu.

974
00:46:10,059 --> 00:46:11,239
[SPEAKER_00] Trajno.

975
00:46:11,239 --> 00:46:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] Če taj isti Kristov duh

976
00:46:13,559 --> 00:46:14,760
[SPEAKER_00] sa optuživati tu zaručnicu

977
00:46:14,760 --> 00:46:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] koju da svoj život?

978
00:46:15,639 --> 00:46:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] Neće.

979
00:46:16,460 --> 00:46:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] Nikad to neće napraviti.

980
00:46:17,619 --> 00:46:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] Proroška riječ

981
00:46:20,500 --> 00:46:22,639
[SPEAKER_00] nikad ne dokida slobodu čovjeka,

982
00:46:22,639 --> 00:46:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] nego je umnaža.

983
00:46:24,199 --> 00:46:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Umnaža slobodu.

984
00:46:26,000 --> 00:46:29,139
[SPEAKER_00] Proroška riječ ne zarobljuje.

985
00:46:29,139 --> 00:46:30,920
[SPEAKER_00] U njoj nema krivnje i osude.

986
00:46:30,920 --> 00:46:32,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ona oslobađa.

987
00:46:32,260 --> 00:46:34,699
[SPEAKER_00] Najvažnija stvar,

988
00:46:34,699 --> 00:46:36,300
[SPEAKER_00] kako neće doći do problema

989
00:46:36,300 --> 00:46:38,260
[SPEAKER_00] i pomutnje sa proroškom riječi,

990
00:46:38,260 --> 00:46:39,119
[SPEAKER_00] je sljedeća.

991
00:46:39,119 --> 00:46:42,199
[SPEAKER_00] Isti duh sveti je u meni i u mati.

992
00:46:42,199 --> 00:46:43,760
[SPEAKER_00] I u svima vama.

993
00:46:43,760 --> 00:46:44,639
[SPEAKER_00] Isti duh sveti.

994
00:46:44,639 --> 00:46:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] I to je, Pavao, jedna od stvari

995
00:46:46,820 --> 00:46:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] koje mora korinčanima

996
00:46:48,119 --> 00:46:49,239
[SPEAKER_00] je govoriti.

997
00:46:49,239 --> 00:46:50,159
[SPEAKER_00] Isti je izvor

998
00:46:50,159 --> 00:46:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] i usporedija je onda

999
00:46:51,039 --> 00:46:52,480
[SPEAKER_00] mistično tijelo Kristovo

1000
00:46:52,480 --> 00:46:53,739
[SPEAKER_00] sa tijelom.

1001
00:46:53,739 --> 00:46:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao, ne može

1002
00:46:54,960 --> 00:46:57,219
[SPEAKER_00] mali prst biti manje važan od palca.

1003
00:46:57,219 --> 00:46:59,079
[SPEAKER_00] Niti pamet od srca.

1004
00:47:00,159 --> 00:47:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] I reći, mali prst palcu,

1005
00:47:01,539 --> 00:47:02,239
[SPEAKER_00] ja te ne treba.

1006
00:47:02,239 --> 00:47:03,500
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je jednako,

1007
00:47:03,500 --> 00:47:04,079
[SPEAKER_00] sve je vrijedno,

1008
00:47:04,079 --> 00:47:04,980
[SPEAKER_00] sve ima svoje mjesto.

1009
00:47:04,980 --> 00:47:08,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, kad Matija dođe,

1010
00:47:08,360 --> 00:47:09,800
[SPEAKER_00] ima proročku riječ za mene,

1011
00:47:09,800 --> 00:47:11,760
[SPEAKER_00] jer proroštvo je dar

1012
00:47:11,760 --> 00:47:12,679
[SPEAKER_00] koji nije za mene,

1013
00:47:12,679 --> 00:47:13,500
[SPEAKER_00] nego za crkvu,

1014
00:47:13,500 --> 00:47:14,079
[SPEAKER_00] za druge,

1015
00:47:14,079 --> 00:47:14,820
[SPEAKER_00] a mi smo crkva,

1016
00:47:14,820 --> 00:47:15,340
[SPEAKER_00] nije crkva,

1017
00:47:15,340 --> 00:47:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] ova ustanova.

1018
00:47:16,460 --> 00:47:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] I kad on ima proročku riječ za mene,

1019
00:47:18,940 --> 00:47:20,860
[SPEAKER_00] ja ga ne slušam slijepo.

1020
00:47:20,860 --> 00:47:21,840
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

1021
00:47:21,840 --> 00:47:22,960
[SPEAKER_00] Jer isti duh

1022
00:47:22,960 --> 00:47:24,159
[SPEAKER_00] koji je njemu to objavio

1023
00:47:24,159 --> 00:47:24,780
[SPEAKER_00] je i u meni.

1024
00:47:24,780 --> 00:47:26,300
[SPEAKER_00] I meni će objaviti.

1025
00:47:26,300 --> 00:47:27,719
[SPEAKER_00] I meni će potvrditi.

1026
00:47:27,719 --> 00:47:30,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ali Bog nekad treba

1027
00:47:30,079 --> 00:47:31,139
[SPEAKER_00] preko njega reći

1028
00:47:31,139 --> 00:47:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] da bi ja ušao u svoju sobu

1029
00:47:33,539 --> 00:47:35,780
[SPEAKER_00] i onda kleknuo pred gospodine

1030
00:47:35,780 --> 00:47:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] i rekao,

1031
00:47:36,079 --> 00:47:36,400
[SPEAKER_00] oče,

1032
00:47:36,400 --> 00:47:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] jel je ovo riječ o tebe?

1033
00:47:37,500 --> 00:47:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ja imam

1034
00:47:39,460 --> 00:47:41,219
[SPEAKER_00] apsolutnu odgovornost

1035
00:47:41,219 --> 00:47:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] za prihvaćanje

1036
00:47:42,019 --> 00:47:42,980
[SPEAKER_00] proročke riječi.

1037
00:47:42,980 --> 00:47:44,659
[SPEAKER_00] Nitko ne može reći

1038
00:47:44,659 --> 00:47:45,360
[SPEAKER_00] on mi je rekao.

1039
00:47:45,360 --> 00:47:46,300
[SPEAKER_00] Niko.

1040
00:47:46,300 --> 00:47:47,940
[SPEAKER_00] I ne smije.

1041
00:47:47,940 --> 00:47:50,559
[SPEAKER_00] Vi kad primate proročku riječ

1042
00:47:50,559 --> 00:47:52,280
[SPEAKER_00] ide u vašu osobnu molitv

1043
00:47:52,280 --> 00:47:53,480
[SPEAKER_00] jer imate odgovornost za nju.

1044
00:47:53,480 --> 00:47:55,099
[SPEAKER_00] Isti Bog,

1045
00:47:55,099 --> 00:47:55,800
[SPEAKER_00] isti duh sveti

1046
00:47:55,800 --> 00:47:56,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji je u meni

1047
00:47:56,340 --> 00:47:57,820
[SPEAKER_00] ili mi je već to stavio na srce

1048
00:47:57,820 --> 00:47:58,940
[SPEAKER_00] pa mi je to potvrda

1049
00:47:58,940 --> 00:48:00,699
[SPEAKER_00] ili tek treba mući

1050
00:48:00,699 --> 00:48:01,820
[SPEAKER_00] i doći do toga.

1051
00:48:01,820 --> 00:48:04,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ali neću poslušati Matiju

1052
00:48:04,880 --> 00:48:06,760
[SPEAKER_00] nego ću ući u sobu

1053
00:48:06,760 --> 00:48:07,860
[SPEAKER_00] i poslušat ću Boga.

1054
00:48:07,860 --> 00:48:09,860
[SPEAKER_00] I ona neće biti Matija

1055
00:48:09,860 --> 00:48:10,780
[SPEAKER_00] mi je prorokovao

1056
00:48:10,780 --> 00:48:12,460
[SPEAKER_00] nego Bog mi je objavio.

1057
00:48:12,460 --> 00:48:14,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Bog želi pričati s menom.

1058
00:48:14,420 --> 00:48:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] Po krštenju sam osposobljen za to.

1059
00:48:16,539 --> 00:48:18,760
[SPEAKER_00] Znate koliko ljudi

1060
00:48:18,760 --> 00:48:20,480
[SPEAKER_00] se odriče svoje odgovornosti.

1061
00:48:20,559 --> 00:48:21,099
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek je lakše

1062
00:48:21,099 --> 00:48:22,460
[SPEAKER_00] ko jeva ili Adam

1063
00:48:22,460 --> 00:48:23,860
[SPEAKER_00] ova žena mi je dala jesti.

1064
00:48:23,860 --> 00:48:25,519
[SPEAKER_00] Nema toga s Kristom.

1065
00:48:25,519 --> 00:48:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si kralj po krštenju

1066
00:48:27,159 --> 00:48:28,400
[SPEAKER_00] upravljaš svojim životom

1067
00:48:28,400 --> 00:48:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] sposoban si za samostalnost

1068
00:48:30,539 --> 00:48:31,699
[SPEAKER_00] za odluke

1069
00:48:31,699 --> 00:48:33,099
[SPEAKER_00] za upravljati sobom.

1070
00:48:33,099 --> 00:48:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je i s proroštvom.

1071
00:48:35,119 --> 00:48:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] Kad primiš proroštvo

1072
00:48:36,079 --> 00:48:38,199
[SPEAKER_00] ideš kao kralj u svoju sobu

1073
00:48:38,199 --> 00:48:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] i pričaš sa svojim ocem.

1074
00:48:40,000 --> 00:48:41,179
[SPEAKER_00] Šta da napravi?

1075
00:48:41,179 --> 00:48:43,340
[SPEAKER_00] Preuzimaš potpunu odgovornost

1076
00:48:43,340 --> 00:48:44,179
[SPEAKER_00] za ono što je izrečeno.

1077
00:48:44,179 --> 00:48:46,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ali puno je lakše biti slijep

1078
00:48:46,800 --> 00:48:48,699
[SPEAKER_00] i prebaciva odgovornost na druge.

1079
00:48:50,699 --> 00:48:52,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je ovo zapamtite

1080
00:48:52,199 --> 00:48:53,800
[SPEAKER_00] da je potpuna odgovornost na vama

1081
00:48:53,800 --> 00:48:55,280
[SPEAKER_00] da ste sposobni razlučiti

1082
00:48:55,280 --> 00:48:56,280
[SPEAKER_00] čuti Boži glas

1083
00:48:56,280 --> 00:48:57,119
[SPEAKER_00] kad primite proroštvo

1084
00:48:57,119 --> 00:48:59,159
[SPEAKER_00] onda neće biti prevara

1085
00:48:59,159 --> 00:49:01,179
[SPEAKER_00] neće biti lažnih proroka.

1086
00:49:01,179 --> 00:49:02,639
[SPEAKER_00] I nećemo ima ni problema.

1087
00:49:02,639 --> 00:49:03,400
[SPEAKER_00] I da ih ima

1088
00:49:03,400 --> 00:49:04,900
[SPEAKER_00] nećemo ima problema.

1089
00:49:04,900 --> 00:49:06,940
[SPEAKER_00] Zamislite sada u crkvi

1090
00:49:06,940 --> 00:49:09,019
[SPEAKER_00] da odgajamo vjernike

1091
00:49:09,019 --> 00:49:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] za kraljevsku čast po krštenju.

1092
00:49:13,480 --> 00:49:14,719
[SPEAKER_00] Patijan, pastir, dođe

1093
00:49:14,719 --> 00:49:17,219
[SPEAKER_00] i onda ljudi često gledaju

1094
00:49:17,219 --> 00:49:18,320
[SPEAKER_00] svećanike i biskupe

1095
00:49:18,320 --> 00:49:19,840
[SPEAKER_00] koja da su mali bogovi na zemlji.

1096
00:49:19,840 --> 00:49:23,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jest njehova služba prekrasna

1097
00:49:23,380 --> 00:49:24,679
[SPEAKER_00] ali oni su tu da služe.

1098
00:49:24,679 --> 00:49:25,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ne da vladaju.

1099
00:49:25,900 --> 00:49:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] Nisu oni moćnici

1100
00:49:26,960 --> 00:49:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] koji mogu nama nešto

1101
00:49:28,300 --> 00:49:29,420
[SPEAKER_00] nad nama vladaju.

1102
00:49:29,420 --> 00:49:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su tu da nam peru noge

1103
00:49:30,539 --> 00:49:31,159
[SPEAKER_00] da nas služe.

1104
00:49:31,159 --> 00:49:32,119
[SPEAKER_00] Isto kao svak od nas

1105
00:49:32,119 --> 00:49:32,900
[SPEAKER_00] kad dobije službu.

1106
00:49:32,900 --> 00:49:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] To nije vlasti

1107
00:49:34,599 --> 00:49:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] nego to je služba.

1108
00:49:36,079 --> 00:49:37,800
[SPEAKER_00] Služba uključuje služenje.

1109
00:49:37,800 --> 00:49:40,719
[SPEAKER_00] Kad mi neko od pastira dođe

1110
00:49:40,719 --> 00:49:42,760
[SPEAKER_00] i pokuša bilo kakvu glupost,

1111
00:49:42,760 --> 00:49:43,760
[SPEAKER_00] manipulaciju,

1112
00:49:43,760 --> 00:49:46,500
[SPEAKER_00] bilo što od mene tražiti,

1113
00:49:46,500 --> 00:49:48,719
[SPEAKER_00] prvo što treba reći

1114
00:49:48,719 --> 00:49:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] paajda stani.

1115
00:49:49,559 --> 00:49:52,920
[SPEAKER_00] Odlazim u sobu

1116
00:49:52,920 --> 00:49:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] provjerit tvoju riječ.

1117
00:49:53,920 --> 00:49:56,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ulazim u hram svoga tijela.

1118
00:49:56,280 --> 00:49:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ulazim u dubine svoga duha

1119
00:49:58,440 --> 00:50:00,219
[SPEAKER_00] gdje isti duh je u tebi i u meni

1120
00:50:00,219 --> 00:50:01,719
[SPEAKER_00] koji je dao tebi tu službu

1121
00:50:01,719 --> 00:50:02,820
[SPEAKER_00] i pozvao u mene,

1122
00:50:02,820 --> 00:50:03,920
[SPEAKER_00] u moju službu.

1123
00:50:03,920 --> 00:50:05,980
[SPEAKER_00] Bog mi to mora potvrditi.

1124
00:50:05,980 --> 00:50:07,780
[SPEAKER_00] Znate koliko bi bilo

1125
00:50:07,780 --> 00:50:08,940
[SPEAKER_00] manje gluposti u crkvi.

1126
00:50:08,940 --> 00:50:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] Manje pedofilije, skandala.

1127
00:50:10,719 --> 00:50:13,719
[SPEAKER_00] Moramo se izgraditi

1128
00:50:13,719 --> 00:50:15,420
[SPEAKER_00] u svome identitetu.

1129
00:50:15,420 --> 00:50:16,820
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je sinostvo ključ.

1130
00:50:16,820 --> 00:50:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] Niko nije vrijedni od nikoga.

1131
00:50:19,039 --> 00:50:19,840
[SPEAKER_00] Niko.

1132
00:50:19,840 --> 00:50:21,280
[SPEAKER_00] Svi smo jednako vrijedni Bogu.

1133
00:50:21,280 --> 00:50:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] Za svakog je jednako umro.

1134
00:50:22,920 --> 00:50:24,900
[SPEAKER_00] Što neko drugi posebni

1135
00:50:24,900 --> 00:50:25,719
[SPEAKER_00] nosi veći križ,

1136
00:50:25,719 --> 00:50:26,659
[SPEAKER_00] vrši veću službu.

1137
00:50:26,659 --> 00:50:27,940
[SPEAKER_00] Boga to, ne znamo,

1138
00:50:27,940 --> 00:50:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] ne gleda tako stvari.

1139
00:50:28,960 --> 00:50:32,920
[SPEAKER_00] A kaže Pavao,

1140
00:50:32,920 --> 00:50:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] jako važnu rečenicu,

1141
00:50:36,420 --> 00:50:38,199
[SPEAKER_00] čeznite za darima duha,

1142
00:50:38,199 --> 00:50:40,119
[SPEAKER_00] a najvećima da prorokujete.

1143
00:50:40,119 --> 00:50:42,280
[SPEAKER_00] Kad Pavao

1144
00:50:42,280 --> 00:50:43,980
[SPEAKER_00] susreće korinčanima

1145
00:50:43,980 --> 00:50:45,679
[SPEAKER_00] u njihovoj nezrelosti,

1146
00:50:45,679 --> 00:50:46,420
[SPEAKER_00] infantilnosti,

1147
00:50:46,420 --> 00:50:48,719
[SPEAKER_00] on kaže,

1148
00:50:48,719 --> 00:50:50,340
[SPEAKER_00] ako već imate potrebu

1149
00:50:50,340 --> 00:50:51,460
[SPEAKER_00] vrednovati neki dar,

1150
00:50:51,460 --> 00:50:53,719
[SPEAKER_00] proroštvo je najvažnije

1151
00:50:53,719 --> 00:50:55,420
[SPEAKER_00] zbog njegove korisnosti.

1152
00:50:59,199 --> 00:51:00,860
[SPEAKER_00] Njegaj proroštvo je stavio

1153
00:51:00,860 --> 00:51:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] na vrh svih karizmi.

1154
00:51:02,000 --> 00:51:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] Znate zašto?

1155
00:51:02,619 --> 00:51:03,880
[SPEAKER_00] Samo zato što izgrađuje.

1156
00:51:03,880 --> 00:51:08,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ako Bog nešto voli,

1157
00:51:08,340 --> 00:51:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] voli izgranju svoje crkve.

1158
00:51:09,619 --> 00:51:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tomo je na vrhu.

1159
00:51:12,000 --> 00:51:13,739
[SPEAKER_00] I zato moramo čezniti.

1160
00:51:13,739 --> 00:51:14,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ali Pavao opet,

1161
00:51:14,820 --> 00:51:16,260
[SPEAKER_00] u istoj rečenici kaže,

1162
00:51:16,260 --> 00:51:17,300
[SPEAKER_00] težite za ljubavlju,

1163
00:51:17,300 --> 00:51:18,300
[SPEAKER_00] to je rečenica nakon

1164
00:51:18,300 --> 00:51:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] prve korinčanima 13,

1165
00:51:19,500 --> 00:51:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] nakon hvalospjeva ljubavi.

1166
00:51:21,000 --> 00:51:22,840
[SPEAKER_00] Pavlu je jako važno

1167
00:51:22,840 --> 00:51:23,159
[SPEAKER_00] da kaže,

1168
00:51:23,159 --> 00:51:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] sve je super,

1169
00:51:24,199 --> 00:51:24,820
[SPEAKER_00] sve je važno.

1170
00:51:24,820 --> 00:51:25,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo da je važno,

1171
00:51:25,579 --> 00:51:26,900
[SPEAKER_00] morate vruće čezni zatim.

1172
00:51:26,900 --> 00:51:27,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja želim da to želite,

1173
00:51:27,960 --> 00:51:29,139
[SPEAKER_00] Bog želi da to želite.

1174
00:51:29,139 --> 00:51:30,019
[SPEAKER_00] To je jako važno.

1175
00:51:30,019 --> 00:51:31,940
[SPEAKER_00] Karizme su ogromne,

1176
00:51:31,940 --> 00:51:33,699
[SPEAKER_00] važne za život crkve.

1177
00:51:33,699 --> 00:51:35,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ali jedino u kontekstu ljubavi.

1178
00:51:35,760 --> 00:51:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedini kontekst i okvir

1179
00:51:40,139 --> 00:51:41,699
[SPEAKER_00] gdje karizme smiju operirati.

1180
00:51:41,699 --> 00:51:44,739
[SPEAKER_00] Kad koristite karizme bez ljubavi,

1181
00:51:44,739 --> 00:51:46,019
[SPEAKER_00] to je ajme meni.

1182
00:51:46,019 --> 00:51:48,139
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka istina,

1183
00:51:48,139 --> 00:51:49,820
[SPEAKER_00] a ne može bi istina bez ljubavi,

1184
00:51:49,820 --> 00:51:51,300
[SPEAKER_00] ali koliko istine bez ljubavi

1185
00:51:51,300 --> 00:51:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] se danas u crkvi govori.

1186
00:51:54,940 --> 00:51:56,320
[SPEAKER_00] A bez duha proročkoga

1187
00:51:56,320 --> 00:51:58,739
[SPEAKER_00] ne možete uopće otkriti dubinu istine.

1188
00:51:58,739 --> 00:52:00,300
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je duh koji otkriva

1189
00:52:00,300 --> 00:52:00,980
[SPEAKER_00] tajne Božje,

1190
00:52:00,980 --> 00:52:01,980
[SPEAKER_00] tajne Božje srca,

1191
00:52:01,980 --> 00:52:02,699
[SPEAKER_00] Božje srce,

1192
00:52:02,699 --> 00:52:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] koji otkriva oca.

1193
00:52:04,039 --> 00:52:07,880
[SPEAKER_00] Neizmjerno važan dar.

1194
00:52:07,880 --> 00:52:10,159
[SPEAKER_00] Sposobni ste slušati Božji glas

1195
00:52:10,159 --> 00:52:11,079
[SPEAKER_00] za druge.

1196
00:52:11,079 --> 00:52:13,139
[SPEAKER_00] Svi imate dar proroštva.

1197
00:52:13,139 --> 00:52:15,059
[SPEAKER_00] Morate vruće čezniti za njim.

1198
00:52:15,059 --> 00:52:17,179
[SPEAKER_00] Morate ga aktivirati,

1199
00:52:17,179 --> 00:52:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] morate u njemu sazrijevat,

1200
00:52:18,539 --> 00:52:19,980
[SPEAKER_00] morate se u njemu formirati.

1201
00:52:19,980 --> 00:52:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] Bićete ko bebe često puta,

1202
00:52:22,380 --> 00:52:23,960
[SPEAKER_00] nezgrapno molit ćete svakako.

1203
00:52:24,159 --> 00:52:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] nećete moliti super kolara danas,

1204
00:52:25,960 --> 00:52:26,719
[SPEAKER_00] odmah iz prve.

1205
00:52:26,719 --> 00:52:28,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ali doći ćete do toga.

1206
00:52:28,860 --> 00:52:30,360
[SPEAKER_00] Doći ćete.

1207
00:52:30,360 --> 00:52:31,519
[SPEAKER_00] Možda ne zati jedan danas,

1208
00:52:31,519 --> 00:52:32,079
[SPEAKER_00] dvi godine.

1209
00:52:32,079 --> 00:52:34,860
[SPEAKER_00] A ono što je još ljepše,

1210
00:52:34,860 --> 00:52:36,699
[SPEAKER_00] što možete čuti Božji glas za druge,

1211
00:52:36,699 --> 00:52:39,639
[SPEAKER_00] i morate i ljepše čuti ga prvo za sebe.

1212
00:52:39,639 --> 00:52:40,820
[SPEAKER_00] Jer kako voliš sebe,

1213
00:52:40,820 --> 00:52:41,760
[SPEAKER_00] tako što voli drugoga.

1214
00:52:41,760 --> 00:52:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti možeš čuti Božji glas za sebe.

1215
00:52:44,079 --> 00:52:45,699
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ti može da proročku riječ za tebe.

1216
00:52:45,699 --> 00:52:50,559
[SPEAKER_00] I često puta ta proročka riječ je vezana uz vaši identite.

1217
00:52:50,559 --> 00:52:51,440
[SPEAKER_00] To je najvažnije.

1218
00:52:51,440 --> 00:52:54,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ti moraš prvi ču da si sin i djete,

1219
00:52:54,780 --> 00:52:55,699
[SPEAKER_00] i da te Bog voli.

1220
00:52:55,699 --> 00:52:57,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ti moraš primiti proročku riječ,

1221
00:52:57,699 --> 00:52:58,139
[SPEAKER_00] remu,

1222
00:52:58,139 --> 00:53:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] ako imaš ranu odbačenosti.

1223
00:53:02,599 --> 00:53:03,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ma dođi u tu sobu.

1224
00:53:03,699 --> 00:53:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ti čuješ da te Bog voli,

1225
00:53:05,960 --> 00:53:07,280
[SPEAKER_00] da te nikad neće ostaviti,

1226
00:53:07,280 --> 00:53:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] pa ne može živjeti i rana,

1227
00:53:09,380 --> 00:53:10,820
[SPEAKER_00] i otkrivenje u istoj osobi.

1228
00:53:10,820 --> 00:53:11,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može.

1229
00:53:11,219 --> 00:53:14,900
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je ta proročka riječ,

1230
00:53:14,900 --> 00:53:18,059
[SPEAKER_00] moramo se osposobiti po našem krištenju

1231
00:53:18,059 --> 00:53:19,679
[SPEAKER_00] za osluškivanje riječi Božje.

1232
00:53:19,679 --> 00:53:21,039
[SPEAKER_00] Da budemo proroci.

1233
00:53:21,039 --> 00:53:22,320
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo za sebe, onda i za druge.

1234
00:53:22,320 --> 00:53:25,800
[SPEAKER_00] Puno toga, to je treća razina.

1235
00:53:25,800 --> 00:53:27,960
[SPEAKER_00] Puno je toga.

1236
00:53:27,960 --> 00:53:28,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam danas,

1237
00:53:28,739 --> 00:53:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] leluja po svemu,

1238
00:53:29,960 --> 00:53:32,199
[SPEAKER_00] ima toga stvari koje sam htio reći,

1239
00:53:32,239 --> 00:53:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] a ne moguće reći u jednom nagovoru.

1240
00:53:33,619 --> 00:53:35,840
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, rekli smo da je prvo po krištenju

1241
00:53:35,840 --> 00:53:36,480
[SPEAKER_00] imamo službu,

1242
00:53:36,480 --> 00:53:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] da smo svi proroci po krištenju.

1243
00:53:38,079 --> 00:53:40,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kršteni smo u Hristovu proročku službu.

1244
00:53:40,800 --> 00:53:43,420
[SPEAKER_00] Druga je razina koja izvira iz krištenja,

1245
00:53:43,420 --> 00:53:44,900
[SPEAKER_00] da imamo svi dar proroštva,

1246
00:53:44,900 --> 00:53:46,360
[SPEAKER_00] da svi možemo čuti Božji glas.

1247
00:53:46,360 --> 00:53:47,739
[SPEAKER_00] I treća razina,

1248
00:53:47,739 --> 00:53:49,300
[SPEAKER_00] Efežani 4,

1249
00:53:49,300 --> 00:53:52,099
[SPEAKER_00] neke dade Bog za proroke.

1250
00:53:52,099 --> 00:53:55,300
[SPEAKER_00] Svi možemo prorokovati.

1251
00:53:55,300 --> 00:53:56,840
[SPEAKER_00] Svi smo po krištenju proroci,

1252
00:53:56,840 --> 00:54:00,420
[SPEAKER_00] ali neki su proroci u užem smislu te riječi.

1253
00:54:01,320 --> 00:54:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] Danas neću o njima pričati.

1254
00:54:02,619 --> 00:54:06,579
[SPEAKER_00] Njih se s razlogom crkva boje,

1255
00:54:06,579 --> 00:54:07,940
[SPEAKER_00] ako su nezreli, neformirani.

1256
00:54:07,940 --> 00:54:10,460
[SPEAKER_00] Puno proroka je napravilo gluposti.

1257
00:54:10,460 --> 00:54:10,739
[SPEAKER_00] Puno.

1258
00:54:10,739 --> 00:54:14,519
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, prireka sam za Montana 3. stoljeće.

1259
00:54:14,519 --> 00:54:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] Skoro čovjek uništio crkvu

1260
00:54:15,960 --> 00:54:17,719
[SPEAKER_00] u ime svog proroštva i svog otkrivenja.

1261
00:54:18,719 --> 00:54:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ti ljudi su ključni da bi crkva živjela punim plučima.

1262
00:54:23,199 --> 00:54:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ih moramo prepoznat.

1263
00:54:25,400 --> 00:54:27,079
[SPEAKER_00] Crkva ne mi.

1264
00:54:27,079 --> 00:54:28,559
[SPEAKER_00] Mora ih formirat.

1265
00:54:28,559 --> 00:54:30,139
[SPEAKER_00] Mora im dat prostor.

1266
00:54:31,340 --> 00:54:34,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može crkva biti crkva upravitelja i učitelja.

1267
00:54:34,679 --> 00:54:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] I onda se zadovoljimo s tim službama.

1268
00:54:37,380 --> 00:54:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] Odrađujemo sve kao upravitelji.

1269
00:54:39,940 --> 00:54:41,719
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo sakramenti.

1270
00:54:41,719 --> 00:54:43,320
[SPEAKER_00] Red, sprovod.

1271
00:54:43,320 --> 00:54:46,039
[SPEAKER_00] Krštenje, vjenčanje.

1272
00:54:46,440 --> 00:54:47,860
[SPEAKER_00] Euharistija, ispovjed.

1273
00:54:47,860 --> 00:54:50,360
[SPEAKER_00] Upravljamo financijama.

1274
00:54:50,360 --> 00:54:52,219
[SPEAKER_00] Zbrajamo bilancu.

1275
00:54:52,219 --> 00:54:53,239
[SPEAKER_00] Plaćamo režije.

1276
00:54:53,239 --> 00:54:56,099
[SPEAKER_00] Upravljamo ljudima resursima, katehezama.

1277
00:54:56,099 --> 00:54:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] Super smo upravitelji.

1278
00:54:58,460 --> 00:55:00,840
[SPEAKER_00] I poučavamo.

1279
00:55:00,840 --> 00:55:02,980
[SPEAKER_00] Držimo te vjeronauke za djecu.

1280
00:55:02,980 --> 00:55:04,900
[SPEAKER_00] I to može funkcionirati.

1281
00:55:04,900 --> 00:55:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo da crkva može biti neplodna.

1282
00:55:07,420 --> 00:55:09,679
[SPEAKER_00] Neplodna.

1283
00:55:09,679 --> 00:55:12,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je samo jedna dobra platforma da se nešto dobro dogodi.

1284
00:55:12,260 --> 00:55:13,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nije plodna.

1285
00:55:13,420 --> 00:55:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi to mogla, mora se otvoriti proročkom duhu.

1286
00:55:16,219 --> 00:55:18,960
[SPEAKER_00] U djelovanju proročkog duha po krštenju svih nas.

1287
00:55:18,960 --> 00:55:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mora se probuditi i biti svjesna da je sposobna osluškivati Boži glas.

1288
00:55:24,000 --> 00:55:26,400
[SPEAKER_00] I sad to možemo pojedinačno, možemo kao grupa.

1289
00:55:26,400 --> 00:55:29,639
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo osluškivati Boži proročku riječ za vašu zajednicu.

1290
00:55:29,639 --> 00:55:32,280
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ćemo živiti po otkrivenjima po proročkoj riječi.

1291
00:55:32,280 --> 00:55:36,019
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ćemo kao zajednica donositi odluku i smjer i ostvarivati svoju viziju

1292
00:55:36,019 --> 00:55:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] kao ponome što Bog objavlja u svojoj proročkoj riječi.

1293
00:55:38,380 --> 00:55:40,199
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo biti proročki narod.

1294
00:55:41,619 --> 00:55:45,820
[SPEAKER_00] Bog želi proročku riječ izgovoriti nad Zagrebom, nad mojom obitelji,

1295
00:55:45,820 --> 00:55:50,300
[SPEAKER_00] nad hrvatskim narodom, nad svakom grupom, nad svakim pojedincem.

1296
00:55:50,300 --> 00:55:54,900
[SPEAKER_00] Proročki duh je puna ga je zemlja, on prožima cijelu zemlju.

1297
00:55:54,900 --> 00:55:56,860
[SPEAKER_00] Živi u svakom vjerniku.

1298
00:55:58,199 --> 00:56:01,019
[SPEAKER_00] Zavisite koliko toga Bog želi reći, a mi ga ne slušamo,

1299
00:56:01,019 --> 00:56:04,800
[SPEAKER_00] jer ne vjerujemo da želi pričati, jer ne znamo da smo po krštenju proroci.

1300
00:56:04,800 --> 00:56:05,940
[SPEAKER_00] I to je stražno.

1301
00:56:05,940 --> 00:56:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato ja želim da se izgradi ta proročka kultura,

1302
00:56:09,000 --> 00:56:11,519
[SPEAKER_00] da nam to postane normalno.

1303
00:56:11,519 --> 00:56:17,280
[SPEAKER_00] Počećemo siguro u našim zajednicama i to se mora preljevat na sve strukture.

1304
00:56:17,280 --> 00:56:20,820
[SPEAKER_00] I tu i siguro obnova u Duhu Svetog ima veliku ulogu.

1305
00:56:20,820 --> 00:56:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] I mi smo šansa za crkvu.

1306
00:56:23,199 --> 00:56:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] I u ovom smislu ima prava šansa kad bi bar jedna stvar kad bi uspili

1307
00:56:27,880 --> 00:56:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] otkriti o tajstvo krštenja vjernicima.

1308
00:56:30,539 --> 00:56:31,139
[SPEAKER_00] Samo to.

1309
00:56:31,139 --> 00:56:33,440
[SPEAKER_00] Da smo svećenici, proroci, kraljevi.

1310
00:56:33,440 --> 00:56:37,579
[SPEAKER_00] I jedna slika da vam bude možda bliska na našem vremenu, jer smo mi mladim.

1311
00:56:37,579 --> 00:56:43,559
[SPEAKER_00] Tolkien, gospodar prsteno, svi ste gledali, tako?

1312
00:56:43,559 --> 00:56:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] Tolkien vam, ne znam koliko svjesno,

1313
00:56:49,699 --> 00:56:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] bazira cijelu svoju prstenovu družinu na trolistu svećenik prorok kralja.

1314
00:56:53,920 --> 00:56:56,139
[SPEAKER_00] Kralja svi znate, Aragorn.

1315
00:56:56,139 --> 00:57:00,480
[SPEAKER_00] Figura kralja u potpunosti prekrasno, prekrasno opisan.

1316
00:57:00,480 --> 00:57:04,340
[SPEAKER_00] Svećenik, da vidim, ko je?

1317
00:57:04,340 --> 00:57:07,539
[SPEAKER_00] Frodo.

1318
00:57:08,380 --> 00:57:12,719
[SPEAKER_00] Taj mali neznatni čovjek, kao mali neznatni čovjek, Matej, vaš župnik,

1319
00:57:12,719 --> 00:57:15,760
[SPEAKER_00] Boga osposobljuje...

1320
00:57:15,760 --> 00:57:17,079
[SPEAKER_00] Sorry, Matej.

1321
00:57:17,079 --> 00:57:19,260
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

1322
00:57:19,260 --> 00:57:26,159
[SPEAKER_00] Boga osposobljuje da prinosi sve naše, sve naše, ono što u prinosu darova donesemo,

1323
00:57:26,159 --> 00:57:31,059
[SPEAKER_00] sve naše napore, sva naša htjenja, žrtve, patnje, boli, molitve.

1324
00:57:31,059 --> 00:57:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] Mi stavljao na oltari to svećeniku, ime svih nas prinosi za spasenje svijeta.

1325
00:57:35,159 --> 00:57:39,699
[SPEAKER_00] Nastavlja Kristovu svećeničku službu, Kristovu otkupiteljsku službu,

1326
00:57:39,699 --> 00:57:43,900
[SPEAKER_00] iznova vršimo spomenčin njegove muke smrti iskrsnuća

1327
00:57:43,900 --> 00:57:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] i aktualizira se u današnje vreme ono što Isus naprave za nas pre 2000 godina.

1328
00:57:48,099 --> 00:57:52,199
[SPEAKER_00] I on tako neznatan postaje onaj koji otkupljuje svijet zajedno s Kristom.

1329
00:57:52,199 --> 00:57:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prekrasno.

1330
00:57:53,000 --> 00:57:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] Mali Frodo iz Šajera, onaj kepec, dobiva prsten,

1331
00:57:58,559 --> 00:58:01,699
[SPEAKER_00] cijela sudbina međuzemlja je oko njegovog vrata.

1332
00:58:01,699 --> 00:58:03,500
[SPEAKER_00] Sve ovisi o njegovom uspjehu.

1333
00:58:03,500 --> 00:58:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] To su naša svećenici danas.

1334
00:58:05,119 --> 00:58:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kako prekrasna slika otolikena.

1335
00:58:07,199 --> 00:58:10,820
[SPEAKER_00] Taj lik koji izražava važnost svećeničke službe

1336
00:58:10,820 --> 00:58:12,800
[SPEAKER_00] i zato ih trebamo častiti.

1337
00:58:12,800 --> 00:58:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] Oni rade nešto po Božijem naumu za cijeli svijet,

1338
00:58:17,340 --> 00:58:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] što je od takve neizmjerne važnosti.

1339
00:58:19,119 --> 00:58:22,400
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je Marino Rostrepo rekao da prestane misa na zemlji

1340
00:58:22,400 --> 00:58:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] ili padre je pio, neko, ne znam, da bi sve u mrak otišlo.

1341
00:58:25,699 --> 00:58:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko je misa ovoga važno.

1342
00:58:28,559 --> 00:58:31,860
[SPEAKER_00] I treća proročka služba je opisana u Gandalfu.

1343
00:58:31,860 --> 00:58:34,639
[SPEAKER_00] Gandalf je prorok.

1344
00:58:34,639 --> 00:58:36,500
[SPEAKER_00] Zamislite kako prekrasan poziv.

1345
00:58:36,500 --> 00:58:38,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazi, on uvijek dolazi,

1346
00:58:38,800 --> 00:58:41,820
[SPEAKER_00] kad on hoće, nikad ne znaš ko vjetar ko je puše,

1347
00:58:41,820 --> 00:58:43,559
[SPEAKER_00] gdje go hoćeš, čuješ mu šum,

1348
00:58:43,559 --> 00:58:45,900
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi i odlazi, dolazi uvijek u pravo vrijeme.

1349
00:58:45,900 --> 00:58:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] I zamislite, on ima neke uvide i razumijevanja

1350
00:58:49,099 --> 00:58:51,699
[SPEAKER_00] koje drugi nemaju, ali nema kompletnu sliku.

1351
00:58:51,699 --> 00:58:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] Nego, Bog mu samo daje, budi nadu.

1352
00:58:54,960 --> 00:58:58,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam, u drugom nastavku, on ili ne znam,

1353
00:58:58,900 --> 00:59:00,219
[SPEAKER_00] ali Mary Pippin s njim,

1354
00:59:00,219 --> 00:59:03,019
[SPEAKER_00] i Mary govori sve je gotovo.

1355
00:59:03,019 --> 00:59:05,139
[SPEAKER_00] Gandalf kaže, je li stvarno gotovo?

1356
00:59:05,139 --> 00:59:08,559
[SPEAKER_00] Gandalfu ima neku perspektivu vječnosti,

1357
00:59:08,559 --> 00:59:10,019
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek perspektivu nade,

1358
00:59:10,019 --> 00:59:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek otvara budućnost u nešto,

1359
00:59:12,559 --> 00:59:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] gleda pozitivu.

1360
00:59:13,599 --> 00:59:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš ubiti ta njegov optimizam u njemu,

1361
00:59:16,440 --> 00:59:17,099
[SPEAKER_00] nema šanse.

1362
00:59:17,099 --> 00:59:21,320
[SPEAKER_00] On donosi, ono hrabro je lidere,

1363
00:59:21,320 --> 00:59:22,880
[SPEAKER_00] on vjeruje u Gandalf,

1364
00:59:22,880 --> 00:59:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] ovo ga je Aragorn, on ga prepoznaje.

1365
00:59:24,880 --> 00:59:28,980
[SPEAKER_00] On vidi hobita, drži malo hobita u sebe,

1366
00:59:28,980 --> 00:59:30,219
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, zato jer se boji,

1367
00:59:30,219 --> 00:59:32,159
[SPEAKER_00] jer vidi u njemu ljepotu i jednostavnosti.

1368
00:59:32,159 --> 00:59:35,239
[SPEAKER_00] On kojemu je toliko dano za vidjeti.

1369
00:59:35,239 --> 00:59:38,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ono baš je prekrasan lik,

1370
00:59:38,239 --> 00:59:40,719
[SPEAKER_00] znaš koju prekrasnu ulogu imaju ti proroci.

1371
00:59:41,440 --> 00:59:43,179
[SPEAKER_00] Što im Bog njima daje nešto posebno

1372
00:59:43,179 --> 00:59:46,719
[SPEAKER_00] za nas družinu, za nas dvanaest u crkvi,

1373
00:59:46,719 --> 00:59:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] što je rekao Matej na početku,

1374
00:59:48,500 --> 00:59:49,320
[SPEAKER_00] vaš župnik.

1375
00:59:49,320 --> 00:59:51,239
[SPEAKER_00] Mi koji smo crkva,

1376
00:59:51,239 --> 00:59:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] proroci su sasani dio crkve.

1377
00:59:54,539 --> 00:59:55,840
[SPEAKER_00] Bez njih se ne može.

1378
00:59:55,840 --> 00:59:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] Čak, ja sam se iznadio,

1379
00:59:57,960 --> 00:59:59,440
[SPEAKER_00] moj profesor sad je pokojeni,

1380
00:59:59,440 --> 01:00:00,679
[SPEAKER_00] Božo Lujić,

1381
01:00:00,679 --> 01:00:02,639
[SPEAKER_00] znam da ga vi znate iz ove zajednice,

1382
01:00:02,639 --> 01:00:05,679
[SPEAKER_00] on je rekao da su vremena bez proroka prokleta.

1383
01:00:05,679 --> 01:00:10,739
[SPEAKER_00] Jer oni na poseban način dobivaju

1384
01:00:10,739 --> 01:00:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] otkrivenja za crku,

1385
01:00:12,199 --> 01:00:12,760
[SPEAKER_00] za svijet,

1386
01:00:12,760 --> 01:00:13,519
[SPEAKER_00] za vrijeme.

1387
01:00:13,519 --> 01:00:15,059
[SPEAKER_00] Čitaju znako vremena.

1388
01:00:15,059 --> 01:00:17,239
[SPEAKER_00] Bog im daje točno ono što u ovom vremenu treba.

1389
01:00:17,239 --> 01:00:19,739
[SPEAKER_00] I proroci su zafrkani.

1390
01:00:19,739 --> 01:00:22,119
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Bog im povjerava službu

1391
01:00:22,119 --> 01:00:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] da razore strukture zloga.

1392
01:00:24,599 --> 01:00:26,619
[SPEAKER_00] Da razotkriju laž.

1393
01:00:28,199 --> 01:00:29,119
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su strašni.

1394
01:00:29,119 --> 01:00:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su opasni.

1395
01:00:30,039 --> 01:00:32,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad su formirani, opasni su.

1396
01:00:32,440 --> 01:00:35,239
[SPEAKER_00] Opasni su i kad su ne formirani na drugi način.

1397
01:00:35,239 --> 01:00:38,599
[SPEAKER_00] Bez proroka nema života.

1398
01:00:38,599 --> 01:00:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] U starom zavijetu sliku Boga su proroci donijeli.

1399
01:00:42,860 --> 01:00:44,659
[SPEAKER_00] Bez njih bi bila siromašlost slika Boga.

1400
01:00:44,659 --> 01:00:47,639
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan ga je prorok objavio kao nježnoga.

1401
01:00:47,639 --> 01:00:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan kao silnoga.

1402
01:00:48,960 --> 01:00:50,239
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan kao kralja.

1403
01:00:50,239 --> 01:00:51,320
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan kao oca.

1404
01:00:51,320 --> 01:00:54,639
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su otkrivali veo z Božijeg srca,

1405
01:00:54,639 --> 01:00:56,639
[SPEAKER_00] z Božijeg lica i upoznavali su

1406
01:00:56,639 --> 01:00:58,260
[SPEAKER_00] izabrani narod s tim kakav je Bog.

1407
01:00:58,260 --> 01:01:01,199
[SPEAKER_00] I podnosili su svu muku i težinu zadaće.

1408
01:01:01,199 --> 01:01:02,820
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je išlo preko njihovih leđa.

1409
01:01:02,820 --> 01:01:04,139
[SPEAKER_00] I znate što?

1410
01:01:04,139 --> 01:01:07,559
[SPEAKER_00] Proroci većinom dobivali ponosu.

1411
01:01:07,559 --> 01:01:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] Plaćali bi svojim životom.

1412
01:01:09,440 --> 01:01:10,800
[SPEAKER_00] Svoju službu.

1413
01:01:10,800 --> 01:01:12,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nije Isus rekao

1414
01:01:12,500 --> 01:01:15,059
[SPEAKER_00] Izraele, Izraele, Jeruzaleme, Jeruzaleme.

1415
01:01:15,059 --> 01:01:16,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ubijao si učitelje.

1416
01:01:16,380 --> 01:01:18,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ubijao si apostole.

1417
01:01:18,639 --> 01:01:21,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ubijao si evangelizatore, pastire.

1418
01:01:21,099 --> 01:01:22,360
[SPEAKER_00] Koga su ubijali?

1419
01:01:22,360 --> 01:01:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je on rekao

1420
01:01:24,460 --> 01:01:25,840
[SPEAKER_00] moram u Jeruzalemu umrijeti?

1421
01:01:25,840 --> 01:01:27,760
[SPEAKER_00] Da su proroci u Jeruzalemu umirali.

1422
01:01:28,619 --> 01:01:30,300
[SPEAKER_00] Prorok i služba proroka

1423
01:01:30,300 --> 01:01:32,360
[SPEAKER_00] je toliko snažna za crkvu

1424
01:01:32,360 --> 01:01:33,860
[SPEAKER_00] da on su,

1425
01:01:33,860 --> 01:01:34,900
[SPEAKER_00] Bog preko njega,

1426
01:01:34,900 --> 01:01:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] proročka riječ preko njega,

1427
01:01:36,199 --> 01:01:38,019
[SPEAKER_00] stavlja narod pred izbor.

1428
01:01:38,019 --> 01:01:40,519
[SPEAKER_00] Poput dvosekle mača

1429
01:01:40,519 --> 01:01:41,780
[SPEAKER_00] ta riječ dijeluje

1430
01:01:41,780 --> 01:01:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] da jasno pokaže što je laž,

1431
01:01:44,460 --> 01:01:45,159
[SPEAKER_00] što je grijeh.

1432
01:01:45,159 --> 01:01:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] I prorok jednostavno donosi

1433
01:01:47,880 --> 01:01:48,900
[SPEAKER_00] osudu grijeha.

1434
01:01:48,900 --> 01:01:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] Prorok ne može mirovati.

1435
01:01:50,900 --> 01:01:51,639
[SPEAKER_00] To je jače od njega.

1436
01:01:51,639 --> 01:01:52,960
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je Jeremija rekao.

1437
01:01:52,960 --> 01:01:55,139
[SPEAKER_00] Htje dok mučat, ali ne mogo.

1438
01:01:55,139 --> 01:01:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ta riječ izlazi iz mene.

1439
01:01:57,000 --> 01:01:58,239
[SPEAKER_00] Oć će pukniti u meni.

1440
01:01:58,260 --> 01:02:00,320
[SPEAKER_00] To su vam proroci.

1441
01:02:00,320 --> 01:02:02,300
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su vas snažne pojave,

1442
01:02:02,300 --> 01:02:03,239
[SPEAKER_00] snažne figure.

1443
01:02:03,239 --> 01:02:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] Istina im je iznad svega.

1444
01:02:04,920 --> 01:02:06,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ako imate u zajednici

1445
01:02:06,860 --> 01:02:08,239
[SPEAKER_00] ili prijatelja nekog

1446
01:02:08,239 --> 01:02:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] koji ne može šutiti

1447
01:02:09,500 --> 01:02:11,699
[SPEAKER_00] jer je kad vidi neku laži glupost,

1448
01:02:11,699 --> 01:02:12,960
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo vjerojatno je taj ima

1449
01:02:12,960 --> 01:02:15,480
[SPEAKER_00] proročki poziv.

1450
01:02:15,480 --> 01:02:18,219
[SPEAKER_00] Njega boli briga za vaše prijateljstvo

1451
01:02:18,219 --> 01:02:19,320
[SPEAKER_00] kad je istina ugrožena.

1452
01:02:20,619 --> 01:02:22,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ne želi takve prijatelje lažove.

1453
01:02:22,519 --> 01:02:23,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može živiti u tome.

1454
01:02:23,659 --> 01:02:24,780
[SPEAKER_00] On traže ambijent,

1455
01:02:24,780 --> 01:02:26,199
[SPEAKER_00] istino, ljubivost, iskrenost,

1456
01:02:26,199 --> 01:02:28,440
[SPEAKER_00] otvorenost, predanja, žara.

1457
01:02:28,440 --> 01:02:30,159
[SPEAKER_00] Želi...

1458
01:02:30,159 --> 01:02:31,480
[SPEAKER_00] On se brine za Božje.

1459
01:02:31,480 --> 01:02:33,340
[SPEAKER_00] Bog mu je tako oblikovao srce

1460
01:02:33,340 --> 01:02:34,480
[SPEAKER_00] kroz pustinju,

1461
01:02:34,480 --> 01:02:35,579
[SPEAKER_00] kroz njegov vlastiti život.

1462
01:02:35,579 --> 01:02:36,920
[SPEAKER_00] Često stoji ljudi patnije,

1463
01:02:36,920 --> 01:02:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] boli, tragedije.

1464
01:02:38,380 --> 01:02:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] Svi kao uzmite stari,

1465
01:02:39,599 --> 01:02:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] znači čitajte o prorocima.

1466
01:02:40,739 --> 01:02:41,780
[SPEAKER_00] Napačeni do boli.

1467
01:02:41,780 --> 01:02:44,059
[SPEAKER_00] Pregaženi, ubijeni.

1468
01:02:44,059 --> 01:02:44,780
[SPEAKER_00] Bog dopušta,

1469
01:02:44,780 --> 01:02:46,079
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ih melje.

1470
01:02:46,079 --> 01:02:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] On im stvara kapacitet u srcu

1471
01:02:47,960 --> 01:02:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] da žive tu riječ,

1472
01:02:48,960 --> 01:02:50,260
[SPEAKER_00] da mogu prenijeti tu riječ.

1473
01:02:50,260 --> 01:02:52,820
[SPEAKER_00] I onda plaćaju svojim životom za to.

1474
01:02:52,820 --> 01:02:55,400
[SPEAKER_00] Većina mučenika imala

1475
01:02:55,400 --> 01:02:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] proročko pomazanje nad sobom.

1476
01:02:57,039 --> 01:03:00,179
[SPEAKER_00] Bili su spremni da svoj život do kraja.

1477
01:03:00,179 --> 01:03:02,179
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna od najtežih službi

1478
01:03:02,179 --> 01:03:03,139
[SPEAKER_00] u katoličkoj crkvi,

1479
01:03:03,139 --> 01:03:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] mi je se bojimo.

1480
01:03:04,119 --> 01:03:05,679
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je to tužno,

1481
01:03:05,679 --> 01:03:06,360
[SPEAKER_00] meni je to boli.

1482
01:03:06,360 --> 01:03:08,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ne smijemo se to dozvoliti.

1483
01:03:08,099 --> 01:03:10,219
[SPEAKER_00] Samo da mi to ne dozvolimo,

1484
01:03:10,280 --> 01:03:11,179
[SPEAKER_00] To je već velika stvar.

